Class UtxoTestSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • UtxoTestSet

  • public class UtxoTestSet
extends Object
    UtxoTestSet represent a random created data test set for testing isValid and txHandler methods. Creates an UtxPool ans several transactions, valid, invalid or conflicted Several flags force different types of transactions A UtxoTestSet can be constructed wit by means of a builder: 
     UtxoTestSet.builder()
        .setPeopleSize(10)
        .setUtxoTxNumber(10)
        .setMaxUtxoTxOutput(10)
        .setMaxValue(200)
        .setTxPerTest(10)
        .setMaxInput(10)
        .setMaxOutput(10)
        .setCorruptedPercentage(0)
        .build();
    Author:
    ealbertos
